frames.caption: A woman with a detailed back tattoo stands on a balcony overlooking a futuristic cityscape. Neon lights and advertisements illuminate the skyline, while a flying vehicle hovers in the distance. The scene conveys a sense of mystery and technological advancement.
frames.description: The scene is set in a futuristic city, characterized by tall skyscrapers adorned with bright neon advertisements. The woman, with her back to the viewer, is observing the city from a high vantage point, suggesting a moment of contemplation or anticipation.

frames.caption: A person with a tattoo on their back stands on a balcony overlooking a futuristic cityscape. The skyline is filled with towering buildings and bright neon advertisements, while flying vehicles move through the air.
frames.description: The scene depicts a futuristic urban environment viewed from a high vantage point. The person is gazing out over a bustling city filled with advanced technology and vibrant lights.
